snippet.title: Elysium gameplay (PC Game, 1992)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Elysium, Dos PC game produced by Magic Bytes in 1992 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/elysium/7596/
Elysium is a very nice history game, a very interesting strategy. You must build your army, have enough food for people and more.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Imperialism - https://youtu.be/u1cF-dzLQDo
Civilization 2: Multiplayer Gold Edition - https://youtu.be/cZ63KH6SA5Q
Civilization 3 - https://youtu.be/tg-56eTun34
